Package: laimsdgxllm
Type: Package
Title: R Interface for Batch LLM Extraction on DGX via SLURM
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Corrado",
           family = "Team",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "corrado@example.org")
Author: Corrado Team [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Corrado Team <corrado@example.org>
Description: User-facing R package scaffold for reproducible batch LLM
    inference on a remote DGX environment reachable only through a login
    node, SSH, SLURM jobs, and Singularity/Apptainer containers. The
    package is designed for structured extraction workflows where many
    records share the same prompt template and output schema, while the
    client remains on the user's workstation and persists run metadata in a
    local SQLite registry.
